										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Is the idea of various Pokémon species walking the streets anything you&#8217;ve ever fantasized about? This is so out there, it belongs in a movie. But with the release of Pokémon GO, that formerly inconceivable dream has come true. Finding your favorite Pokémon while you go down the street with your phone is a first of its kind.</p>
<h3>EXPLORE THE REAL WORLD: DISCOVER POKÉMON</h3>
<p>The opportunity to encounter Pokémon in real life is one of the most unique aspects that Pokémon GO can offer its players. That virtual reality has made this a reality is intriguing. All players have to do is hold their smartphone, activate the camera within the game, and embark on their walking adventure. It is also possible to locate your preferred Pokémon by taking a stroll through crowded streets or, on occasion, a new park.</p>
<ul>
<li><em><strong>Explore New Places</strong>: Get outside, walk around, and explore cities and parks to find Pokémon.</em></li>
<li><em><strong>Use AR Mode</strong>: See Pokémon superimposed in real-world settings using AR mode.</em></li>
<li><em><strong>Hatch Eggs</strong>: Hatch eggs as you walk around to get a surprise new Pokémon.</em></li>
<li><em><strong>Spin PokéStops</strong>: Discover and spin PokéStops for useful items to help catch Pokémon.</em></li>
<li><em><strong>Exercise &amp; Adventure:</strong> Exercise and adventure simultaneously while discovering new sights.</em></li>
</ul>
<h3>CATCH POKÉMON: COMPLETE YOUR POKÉDEX</h3>
<p>Games developed on other Pokémon platforms usually use a character-controlled role-playing style. But with Pokémon GO, you will directly become a real Pokémon hunter. A huge collection of hundreds of Pokémon types and many different types has been fully integrated for you to add to your list. Fill it up quickly and show it off to your friends.</p>
<ul>
<li><em><strong>Gotta Catch &#8216;Em All:</strong> Hundreds of Pokémon are available from different generations.</em></li>
<li><em><strong>Register New Pokémon</strong>: Feel immense satisfaction when you finally register a captured or rare Pokémon.</em></li>
<li><em><strong>Increase Catch Chances</strong>: Use berries, great throws, and Ultra Balls to increase your chances of catching Pokémon.</em></li>
<li><em><strong>Evolve &amp; Power Up</strong>: Evolve and power up Pokémon to fill out their evolutions in your Pokédex.</em></li>
<li><em><strong>Show Off Your Pokédex</strong>: Display your completed Pokédex and rare catches to friends.</em></li>
</ul>
<h3>GO BATTLE LEAGUE &#8211; BATTLE OTHER TRAINERS ONLINE FOR BRAGGING RIGHTS AND REWARDS!</h3>
<p>The main character&#8217;s primary goal in the series is to become the world Pokémon training champion, and you are the same. Your mission is to become a true champion with the Pokémon you have caught in the spheres. Intense duels will be created, and you will need to use your Pokémon to confront your opponent&#8217;s Pokémon. Gradually climb higher rankings and reach the top of the list.</p>
<ul>
<li><em><strong>Test Your Skills</strong>: Take part in battles to test your Pokémon fighting skills against real opponents.</em></li>
<li><em><strong>Climb the Ranks</strong>: Unlock new ranks like Ace Trainer and Legend as you win more battles.</em></li>
<li><em><strong>Win Prizes</strong>: Earn Stardust, Rare Candies, and other prizes when you win battles and complete sets.</em></li>
<li><em><strong>Increase Your Rating</strong>: Keep battling to increase your rating and compete against tougher opponents.</em></li>
</ul>
<h3>PARTICIPATE IN RAID BATTLES: TAKE DOWN POWERFUL BOSSES</h3>
<p>If you do not like going head-to-head with other trainers, the combined game mode will be completely suitable. In this game mode, you can combine with 20 different trainers to create a great cooperative battle. A countdown has begun, and you and your teammates will need to defeat the dangerous bosses. Many different rewards await you after wins in Raid Battles.</p>
<ul>
<li><em><strong>Exciting Co-op Battles</strong>: Team up with up to 20 other Trainers for exciting cooperative Raid Battles.</em></li>
<li><em><strong>Defeat Raid Bosses:</strong> Collaborate to take down powerful Raid Bosses before time runs out.</em></li>
<li><em><strong>Deal Big Damage</strong>: Use your most powerful Pokémon&#8217;s best attacks to deal big damage.</em></li>
<li><em><strong>Earn Rare Rewards</strong>: Get rare Candy and TMs to power up and teach new moves to your Pokémon.</em></li>
<li><em><strong>Catch Rare Pokémon</strong>: Raid Battles are the best way to catch Legendary and very rare Pokémon.</em></li>
<li><em><strong>Unlock Bonuses</strong>: Become friends with other Trainers to unlock even greater Raid Battle rewards bonuses.</em></li>
</ul>
